            <title>[CXF-4816] Allow use of @Policy on Service Implementation as alternative to Interface</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-4816</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The PolicyAnnotationListener has a section for registering @Policies from the Impl, so I am changing the type to a Bug as its not workng.&lt;/p&gt;
